OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FKetamine for alcoholics    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ftrial goes to next stage   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A programme of therapy involving the   
OL,6, drug ketamine will be made available to
OL,7, alcoholics in a research project.      
OL,9,FThe University of Exeter-led trial,    
OL,10,Fwith funding of #2.4m, will go ahead at
OL,11,Fseven NHS sites across the UK.         
OL,13,FThe trial will look into whether a     
OL,14,Fcombination of ketamine and therapy    
OL,15,Fcould help alcoholics stay sober for   
OL,16,Flonger.                                
OL,18,FProf Celia Morgan, the academic behind 
OL,19,Fthe research, said there was an "urgent
OL,20,Fneed" for new treatments.              
